title: Zigzag Conversion
example_input: # Example input for Zigzag Conversion
example_output: # Expected output for Zigzag Conversion
description:
Given a string `s` and an integer `numRows`, arrange the characters of the string in a zigzag pattern on a given number of rows and then read the pattern row by row. Return the final string.

Example: Input: s = "PAYPALISHIRING", numRows = 3

P   A   H   N
A P L S I I G
Y   I   R
Output: "PAHNAPLSIIGYIR"
